 ----------
 1. - file type
 2. --- rwx for users
 3. --- rwx for group
 4. --- rwx for others

(4= read, 2= write, 1= execute, 0= no permission)
 777 - full permission for all
 755 - full permission for user, read and execute for group and others
 644 - read and write for user, read for group and others
 600 - read and write for user, no permission for group and others


 chmod db.conf 
